#: inc/related-posts.php:140
msgid ""
"The Related Posts feature works by checking for shared taxonomy terms. If "
"your post has the terms “WordPress” and “Website”, then Related Posts will "
"display other posts that also have the terms “WordPress” and “Website”."
msgstr ""
"Iṣẹ ẹya Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ ti o ni ibatan n ṣiṣẹ nipa ṣayẹwo fun awọn ọrọ "
"taxonomy ti o pin. Ti ifiweranṣẹ rẹ ba ni awọn ọrọ “WordPress” ati "
"“Website”, lẹhinna Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ ti o ni ibatan yoo ṣe afihan awọn "
"ifiweranṣẹ miiran ti o tun ni awọn ọrọ “WordPress” ati “Website”."

